snippet.title: Temple Run: Oz -- Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The most thrilling running experience now comes to the yellow brick road!

Download on the App Store http://bit.ly/WgSWAk
Download on Google Play http://bit.ly/15tVpYH

Disney and Imangi Studios present Temple Run: Oz -- a brand-new endless runner inspired by Temple Run 2 and the film Oz the Great and Powerful! Begin your exhilarating adventure now and see how far you can run!
